# {{RESOURCE_NAME}} Module

Terraform module which creates a `{{RESOURCE_NAME}}` resource on `{{PROVIDER}}`.

## Usage

### Single resource

```hcl
module "{{RESOURCE_VAR}}" {
  source = "./modules/{{SERVICE}}/{{RESOURCE}}"

  {{RESOURCE_VAR}}_name        = "example-{{RESOURCE}}"
  {{RESOURCE_VAR}}_description = "Example {{RESOURCE_NAME}}"
  {{RESOURCE_VAR}}_region      = "<your-region>"

  {{RESOURCE_VAR}}_tags = {
    Environment = "dev"
    Terraform   = "true"
  }
}
```

### Multiple resources (using wrappers)

```hcl
module "{{RESOURCE_VAR}}_multiple" {
  source = "./modules/{{SERVICE}}/{{RESOURCE}}/wrappers"

  defaults = {
    {{RESOURCE_VAR}}_region = "<your-region>"
    {{RESOURCE_VAR}}_tags = {
      Terraform = "true"
    }
  }

  items = {
    example1 = {
      {{RESOURCE_VAR}}_name = "example-{{RESOURCE}}-1"
    }
    example2 = {
      {{RESOURCE_VAR}}_name = "example-{{RESOURCE}}-2"
    }
  }
}
```

